name: BrowZine
description: A browsable newsstand of the library's top journals. Easily find, read, and monitor thousands of scholarly journals directly from your tablet. BrowZine is a tablet-based service that works in tandem with many databases to recreate the experience of browsing and reading a journal. ** How do I start using BrowZine?, <1> From your iPad or Android, download the free iOS or Android app; and install it. <2> When you open BrowZine for the first time, you will see a list of schools; select New York University. <3> Enter your NYU Username and Password.
